OL,3,CCampaigners at Court of Appeal over
OL,4,Ctwo-mile Stonehenge tunnel decision
OL,6,FHe told the Court of Appeal that the
OL,7,Fthen-minister wrongly gave no
OL,8,Fconsideration to the "risk of
OL,9,FStonehenge being delisted" as a World
OL,10,FHeritage Site.
OL,12,FHe also failed to take the Carbon
OL,13,FBudget Delivery Plan and the Net Zero
OL,14,FGrowth Plan into his deliberations, Mr
OL,15,FWolfe said.
