OL,3,CCampaigners at Court of Appeal over
OL,4,Ctwo-mile Stonehenge tunnel decision
OL,6,FMr Wolfe continued in written
OL,7,Fsubmissions: "(Mr Merriman)'s approach
OL,8,Fto environmental impact assessment was
OL,9,Funlawful in relation to the cumulative
OL,10,Feffect of greenhouse gas emissions
OL,11,Ffrom the development consent scheme
OL,12,Fand other committed road schemes."
OL,14,FThe Department for Transport is
OL,15,Fdefending the appeal.
