OL,6,FNational Highways has previously said
OL,7,Fits plan for the tunnel will remove
OL,8,Fthe sight and sound of traffic passing
OL,9,Fthe site and cut journey times.
OL,11,FThe hearing before Sir Keith Lindblom,
OL,12,FLord Justice Lewis and Lord Justice
OL,13,FStuart-Smith is expected to conclude
OL,14,Fon Tuesday, with a decision expected
OL,15,Fin writing at a later date.
